 <span data-ttu-id="7171b-102"><xref:System.Web.ApplicationServices.RoleService>对象可用于读取通过 Windows Communication Foundation (WCF) 服务的用户的角色。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7171b-102">The <xref:System.Web.ApplicationServices.RoleService> object enables you to read a user's roles through a Windows Communication Foundation (WCF) service.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7171b-103">若要使用的角色服务，必须启用 Web 服务器上的角色服务，然后连接到 Web 服务的 WCF 兼容客户端应用程序。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7171b-103">To use the role service, you must enable the role service on a Web server and then connect a WCF-compatible client application to the Web service.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7171b-104">有关如何配置的角色服务的信息，请参阅[如何： 启用 WCF 角色服务](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/d021aa39-4cbf-4450-a3c1-d5573ca7ce8c)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7171b-104">For information about how to configure the role service, see [How to: Enable the WCF Role Service](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/d021aa39-4cbf-4450-a3c1-d5573ca7ce8c).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7171b-105">必须对用户进行身份验证，来读取用户的角色。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7171b-105">The user must be authenticated to read the user's roles.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7171b-106">角色服务适用于任何类型的 ASP.NET 身份验证。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7171b-106">The role service works with any kind of ASP.NET authentication.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7171b-107">有关如何通过 WCF 服务中的用户登录的信息，请参阅[Windows Communication Foundation 身份验证服务概述](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/6e121a28-89e8-4974-88a8-70aaa6a7d52b)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7171b-107">For information about how to log users in through a WCF service, see [Windows Communication Foundation Authentication Service Overview](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/6e121a28-89e8-4974-88a8-70aaa6a7d52b).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7171b-108"><xref:System.Web.ApplicationServices.RoleService>类公开应仅通过 WCF 服务访问的两个方法：<xref:System.Web.ApplicationServices.RoleService.GetRolesForCurrentUser%2A>方法和<xref:System.Web.ApplicationServices.RoleService.IsCurrentUserInRole%2A>方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7171b-108">The <xref:System.Web.ApplicationServices.RoleService> class exposes two methods that should be accessed only through a WCF service: the <xref:System.Web.ApplicationServices.RoleService.GetRolesForCurrentUser%2A> method and the <xref:System.Web.ApplicationServices.RoleService.IsCurrentUserInRole%2A> method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7171b-109"><xref:System.Web.ApplicationServices.RoleService.GetRolesForCurrentUser%2A>方法将返回登录用户的所有角色。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7171b-109">The <xref:System.Web.ApplicationServices.RoleService.GetRolesForCurrentUser%2A> method returns all the roles for the logged-in user.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7171b-110"><xref:System.Web.ApplicationServices.RoleService.IsCurrentUserInRole%2A>方法确定用户是否属于指定角色。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7171b-110">The <xref:System.Web.ApplicationServices.RoleService.IsCurrentUserInRole%2A> method determines whether the user is in a specified role.</span></span>  
  
